Class PersistentObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ardock.moodapp.moodock.lib.data.persistence.objects.PersistentObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IConvertible

    public class PersistentObject
extends Object
implements IConvertible
    The PersistentObject class is the root class of the persistence class hierarchy.

    All persistent objects inherit either directly or indirectly from this class.
